                    <div class="accordion-body">
                      <p>This is a fundraising initiative started in 2017 with the aim of raising funds for school fees, accommodation and food for underprivileged medical students. In 2022, the idea was developed for a charity run to be organized to boost the funds drive. The second annual edition of the LNMB Run will be taking place on 29th April 2023.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="accordion-item">
